  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下Google登录的完整时序图。前端用PKCE流程，先本地生成code verifier和code challenge，然后跳转到Google OAuth拿授权码。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Google OAuth",
        "code",
        "codeVerifier"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以Client自己先生成PKCE参数，然后重定向到Google。那Google回调之后，前端是把code和codeVerifier一起发给后端吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "AuthController",
        "code",
        "codeVerifier"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，POST到/api/auth/google-login，body里带code和codeVerifier。然后AuthController调用GoogleOAuthService去换token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthController",
        "GoogleOAuthService",
        "ExchangeCodeForTokens"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我加上GoogleOAuthService。它内部应该去调Google Token API吧？用那个oauth2.googleapis.com/token端点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GoogleOAuthService",
        "Google Token API",
        "access_token",
        "id_token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，拿到id_token之后，GOS要先用Google Validator验证这个token的签名，解析出sub和email这些claims。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GoogleOAuthService",
        "Google Validator",
        "sub",
        "id_token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "验证通过后，AuthController拿sub去查用户对吧？需要走UserRepository查PostgreSQL。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthController",
        "UserRepository",
        "PostgreSQL",
        "sub",
        "GoogleProviderId"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，FindByGoogleProviderId用sub去查，找到用户后，调用JwtTokenGenerator生成我们自己的authToken，最后Set-Cookie返回给前端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserRepository",
        "JwtTokenGenerator",
        "authToken",
        "userId",
        "cookie"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。我确认了完整的流程：Client生成PKCE→Google授权→回调带code→AuthController收参数→GOS换token并验证→查库确认用户→生成JWT→Cookie返回。所有参与者和消息都画好了。",
